The Second Blacksmith


09 Mar 2020 20:38








Thank you to the outstanding individuals who helped me return to the site after nearly 8 years without an article! This goes doubly so for GerrymanderBassistand many more!

A few spoilers -

TheSpoilers

AccessGranted




1) The [REDACTED] threat is none other than SCP-One Billion, first mentioned in SCP-990.

2) Hattic was chosen because that was the language spoken in one of the locations that's theorized to feature the oldest known blacksmithing site.

3) The Weapon has both physical and pataphysical components.




Thanks for reading!





